---
// Main content for privacy-policy page
---

<section class="privacy-section">
  <div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container-full w-container">
    <div class="privacy-content-wrapper">
      <div class="privacy-header">
        <h1 class="privacy-title">Privacy Policy</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="privacy-content">
        <section class="privacy-block">
          <h2 class="privacy-heading">Introduction</h2>
          <div class="privacy-text">
            <p>Welcome to Blockchain Web Services Inc.'s policy document.</p>
            <p>
              We provide Software as a Service (SaaS) Application Programming Interface (API) solutions focusing on
              blockchain technology. Please read this document carefully to understand our policies and practices
              regarding your information and how we handle it.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="privacy-block">
          <h2 class="privacy-heading">Content Responsibility</h2>
          <div class="privacy-text">
            <p>
              We take utmost care in developing and maintaining the content that is provided through our API services.
              Nevertheless, we cannot guarantee the accuracy, completeness, or quality of the content. While we are
              accountable for the content we publish as per U.S. laws, we are not required to monitor third-party
              information for any indications of illegal activities.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="privacy-block">
          <h2 class="privacy-heading">Data Protection & Privacy</h2>
          <div class="privacy-text">
            <p>
              We are committed to safeguarding the privacy and security of your data. All data transactions are
              encrypted and stored on secure servers. Please refer to our Privacy Policy for a detailed explanation of
              how we collect, use, and safeguard your information.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="privacy-block">
          <h2 class="privacy-heading">API Use & Access</h2>
          <div class="privacy-text">
            <p>
              You are granted a non-exclusive, non-transferable, limited right to access our APIs. Unauthorized access,
              distribution, or replication of our API and its content is strictly prohibited and may result in
              termination of service as well as legal action.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="privacy-block">
          <h2 class="privacy-heading">Compliance & Regulations</h2>
          <div class="privacy-text">
            <p>
              Being a blockchain company operating in the United States, we adhere to all federal and state regulations
              concerning blockchain technology and financial transactions, including but not limited to Anti-Money
              Laundering (AML) and Know Your Customer (KYC) guidelines.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="privacy-block">
          <h2 class="privacy-heading">Intellectual Property</h2>
          <div class="privacy-text">
            <p>
              All intellectual property rights related to our API, website, and any other services provided are owned by
              Blockchain Web Services Inc. and are protected by copyright laws. No part of our services may be copied,
              modified, or distributed without explicit written permission from Blockchain Web Services Inc.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="privacy-block">
          <h2 class="privacy-heading">Third-Party Services</h2>
          <div class="privacy-text">
            <p>
              Our API may integrate with third-party services. We are not responsible for any third-party content,
              policies, or actions. Users are encouraged to read the terms and conditions and privacy policies of
              third-party services when integrated.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="privacy-block">
          <h2 class="privacy-heading">Service Level Agreement (SLA)</h2>
          <div class="privacy-text">
            <p>
              We aim to provide 99.9% uptime for our API services. However, we are not liable for any losses incurred
              due to service interruptions, which may be caused by factors beyond our control. Please refer to our SLA
              for more information.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="privacy-block">
          <h2 class="privacy-heading">Indemnification</h2>
          <div class="privacy-text">
            <p>
              You agree to indemnify, defend, and hold harmless Blockchain Web Services Inc., its officers, directors,
              employees, and agents from and against any claims, actions, or demands arising out of or related to your
              use of our services.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="privacy-block">
          <h2 class="privacy-heading">Amendments</h2>
          <div class="privacy-text">
            <p>
              We reserve the right to amend this policy document at any time. Updated versions will be posted on our
              website, and the date of the latest revision will be stated.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="privacy-block">
          <h2 class="privacy-heading">Contact Us</h2>
          <div class="privacy-text">
            <p>
              For any queries regarding this policy document, please contact us at
              <a href="mailto:info@bws.ninja">info@bws.ninja</a>.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="privacy-block">
          <div class="privacy-text privacy-footer">
            <p><em>Last updated: September 16, 2023</em></p>
            <p>
              By using our API services, you agree to abide by the terms and conditions outlined in this policy
              document.
            </p>
            <p><em>© 2024 Blockchain Web Services. All rights reserved.</em></p>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .privacy-section {
    padding: 80px 0;
    min-height: 60vh;
  }

  .privacy-content-wrapper {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .privacy-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
    padding-bottom: 30px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
  }

  .privacy-title {
    font-size: 48px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }

  .privacy-block {
    margin-bottom: 50px;
  }

  .privacy-heading {
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: #333;
  }

  .privacy-text {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #555;
  }

  .privacy-text p {
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .privacy-text ul {
    margin: 20px 0;
    padding-left: 30px;
  }

  .privacy-text li {
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    list-style-type: disc;
  }

  .privacy-text a {
    color: #0066cc;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .privacy-text a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .privacy-text strong {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #333;
  }

  .privacy-footer {
    margin-top: 60px;
    padding-top: 30px;
    border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .privacy-footer p {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #888;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .privacy-section {
      padding: 60px 20px;
    }

    .privacy-title {
      font-size: 36px;
    }

    .privacy-heading {
      font-size: 24px;
    }

    .privacy-text {
      font-size: 15px;
    }
  }
</style>
